.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH find 1  "find " 
.SH NAME
find \- Search local files
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBfind\fR [\fB\-\-kind\fR] [\fB\-i\fR|\fB\-\-ignore\-case\fR] [\fB\-s\fR|\fB\-\-case\-sensitive\fR] [\fB\-F\fR|\fB\-\-fixed\-strings\fR] [\fB\-p\fR|\fB\-\-full\-path\fR] [\fB\-H\fR|\fB\-\-hidden\fR] [\fB\-L\fR|\fB\-\-follow\-links\fR] [\fB\-a\fR|\fB\-\-absolute\-path\fR] [\fB\-d\fR|\fB\-\-download\fR] [\fB\-\-depth\fR] [\fB\-\-min\-depth\fR] [\fB\-\-max\-depth\fR] [\fB\-\-sizes\fR] [\fB\-\-modified\-within\fR] [\fB\-\-modified\-before\fR] [\fB\-\-time\-modified\fR] [\fB\-e\fR|\fB\-\-extension\fR] [\fB\-\-type\fR] [\fB\-\-threads\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPATTERN\fR> [\fIPATH\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Search local files
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-kind\fR \fI<KIND>\fR [default: glob]

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
exact
.IP \(bu 2
glob
.IP \(bu 2
regex
.RE
.TP
\fB\-i\fR, \fB\-\-ignore\-case\fR
Case insensitive search
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-case\-sensitive\fR
Case sensitive search
.TP
\fB\-F\fR, \fB\-\-fixed\-strings\fR
Treat patterns as literal strings
.TP
\fB\-p\fR, \fB\-\-full\-path\fR
Search full path (default: filename only)
.TP
\fB\-H\fR, \fB\-\-hidden\fR
Search hidden files and directories
.TP
\fB\-L\fR, \fB\-\-follow\-links\fR
Follow symbolic links
.TP
\fB\-a\fR, \fB\-\-absolute\-path\fR
Print absolute paths
.TP
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-download\fR
Exclude sendonly/publicreadonly folders from search
.TP
\fB\-\-depth\fR \fI<DEPTH>\fR
Depth constraints: N, +N (min), \-N (max)
.TP
\fB\-\-min\-depth\fR \fI<MIN_DEPTH>\fR
Alternative min depth notation
.TP
\fB\-\-max\-depth\fR \fI<MAX_DEPTH>\fR
Alternative max depth notation
.TP
\fB\-\-sizes\fR \fI<SIZES>\fR
Size constraints: N, \-N, +N, N%10, +5GB, etc.
.TP
\fB\-\-modified\-within\fR \fI<MODIFIED_WITHIN>\fR
Newer than: \*(Aq3 days\*(Aq, \*(Aq2 weeks\*(Aq
.TP
\fB\-\-modified\-before\fR \fI<MODIFIED_BEFORE>\fR
Older than: \*(Aq3 years\*(Aq, \*(Aq1 month\*(Aq
.TP
\fB\-\-time\-modified\fR \fI<TIME_MODIFIED>\fR
Time modified: \*(Aq\-3 days\*(Aq (newer), \*(Aq+3 days\*(Aq (older)
.TP
\fB\-e\fR, \fB\-\-extension\fR \fI<EXTENSION>\fR
File extensions to include
.TP
\fB\-\-type\fR \fI<FILE_TYPE>\fR
Filter by type: f=file, d=dir, l=symlink
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
f
.IP \(bu 2
d
.IP \(bu 2
l
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-threads\fR \fI<THREADS>\fR [default: 0]
Scanner threads (1 disables parallelism, 0 uses all available CPUs)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIPATTERN\fR>

.TP
[\fIPATH\fR] [default: .]

